org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.api.mediation

Interface MetricsSupport


  • public interface MetricsSupport
    Provides custom statistics support for proxy services, sequences and global artifacts. Statistics are stored in the org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.CustomStatistics MXBean // todo: remove the CustomStatistics MXBean and use the MetricsMXBean
